languages.text: "То мне неведомо. Видения показали лишь бесконечно зеленое море... Живое море. И безумную жажду охотника, преследующего Детей Азуриана. Изгой, твой Путь вновь ведет тебя к звездам — найди наших собратьев и не дай им погибнуть".

traits.locale_text: "То мне неведомо. Видениях показали лишь бесконечно зеленое море... Живое море. И безумную жажду охотника, преследующего Детей Азуриана. Изгой, твой Путь вновь ведет тебя к звездам — найди наших собратьев и не дай им погибнуть".
traits.speaker: JungleWorldEldarSeer_Muaran

languages.text: "That I know not. All that my visions showed me was an infinitely green sea... A living sea. And the maddening thirst of a hunter who was pursuing the Children of Asuryan. Outcast, your Path is taking you toward the stars again. Find our kin and do not let them perish."

languages.text: “我也不知道。我只看到了一片广袤无垠的绿色海洋……一片拥有生命的海洋，还有在阿苏焉的子嗣身后不断追逐的猎人，他对鲜血的渴望，让他陷入了疯狂。流浪者啊，你的道路将再次让你走向群星之中。找到我们的同胞，将他们从死亡之中拯救出来。”
languages.original_text: "That I know not. All that my visions showed me was an infinitely green sea... A living sea. And the maddening thirst of a hunter who was pursuing the Children of Asuryan. Outcast, your Path is taking you toward the stars again. Find our kin and do not let them perish."

traits.speaker: JungleWorldEldarSeer_Muaran

languages.text: "Das weiß ich nicht. Meine Visionen haben mir nur ein endlos grünes Meer gezeigt ... Ein lebendes Meer. Und den rasenden Durst eines Jägers, der die Kinder von Asuryan jagte. Ausgestoßene, Euer Pfad ist es, wieder in die Sterne zu ziehen. Findet unsere Brüder und lasst sie nicht sterben."
languages.original_text: "That I know not. All that my visions showed me was an infinitely green sea... A living sea. And the maddening thirst of a hunter who was pursuing the Children of Asuryan. Outcast, your Path is taking you toward the stars again. Find our kin and do not let them perish."

Ausgestoßene, Euer Pfad ist es, wieder in die Sterne zu ziehen. Findet unsere Brüder und lasst sie nicht sterben."
traits.speaker: JungleWorldEldarSeer_Muaran

languages.text: «Eso lo ignoro. Lo único que me mostraron las visiones fue un océano verde e infinito... Un mar lleno de vida. Y la enloquecedora sed de sangre de un cazador que perseguía a los hijos de Asuryan. Proscrita, tu senda te lleva de nuevo a las estrellas. Encuentra a nuestros congéneres y no permitas que perezcan».
languages.original_text: "That I know not. All that my visions showed me was an infinitely green sea... A living sea. And the maddening thirst of a hunter who was pursuing the Children of Asuryan. Outcast, your Path is taking you toward the stars again. Find our kin and do not let them perish."

traits.speaker: JungleWorldEldarSeer_Muaran

languages.text: « Je l'ignore. Tout ce que mes visions m'ont montré, c'est un océan vert sans limites... Un océan vivant. Et la soif déroutante d'un chasseur qui traquait les enfants d'Asuryan. Errante, votre Voie vous mène une fois encore vers les étoiles. Trouvez les nôtres et sauvez-les de la mort. »
languages.original_text: "That I know not. All that my visions showed me was an infinitely green sea... A living sea. And the maddening thirst of a hunter who was pursuing the Children of Asuryan. Outcast, your Path is taking you toward the stars again. Find our kin and do not let them perish."

Errante, votre Voie vous mène une fois encore vers les étoiles. Trouvez les nôtres et sauvez-les de la mort. »
traits.speaker: JungleWorldEldarSeer_Muaran

languages.text: 「それは分からない。ビジョンが見せてくれたのは、無限に広がる緑の海だった…生きている海。そしてアシュリアンの御子を追うハンターの狂おしい渇きだ。追放者よ、お前の道は再び星々に向かっている。我々の同胞を探し出し、滅亡を阻止して欲しい」
languages.original_text: "That I know not. All that my visions showed me was an infinitely green sea... A living sea. And the maddening thirst of a hunter who was pursuing the Children of Asuryan. Outcast, your Path is taking you toward the stars again. Find our kin and do not let them perish."

languages.text: "Onu bilmiyorum. Görülerimde yalnızca engin, yeşil bir deniz var... Yaşayan bir deniz. Bir de Asuryan'ın Çocukları'nı izleyen avcının kana susamışlığı. Yurtsuz... Yolun yine yıldız yoluyla kesişiyor. Soydaşlarımızı bul, başlarına bir iş gelmesin."
